<noinclude>
==Documentation==
Renders the game page sidebar with structured data pulled from Semantic MediaWiki properties.

This template is called automatically by <code><nowiki>{{GameEnd}}</nowiki></code>.

All data comes from two calls into [[Module:GameSidebar]]: one SMW query for
the page's own properties (details block + fallback lists) and one gb_related
read for the ranked accordions (see the GBRelated extension).

===Sections===
# '''Game details''' - Name, release date, platforms, developer, publisher, genre, theme, franchise, aliases
# '''Related content''' - Accordion sections for Similar Games, Characters, Locations, Concepts, Objects, People
</noinclude><includeonly>
<div class="gb-sidebar-section">
<div class="gb-sidebar-reviews">{{#invoke:ReviewQuery|renderSidebar}}</div>
<div class="gb-sidebar-section-header">Game details</div>
<div class="gb-sidebar-section-content">
{{#invoke:GameSidebar|details}}
</div>
</div>

<div class="gb-sidebar-accordions">
{{#invoke:GameSidebar|accordions}}
</div>
</includeonly>
